_documentation.description: Configuration file for Top 50 US Metropolitan Statistical Areas Economic Health Report
notes: This file contains all FRED API codes and configuration for pulling economic data
Each metro has a unique set of FRED series IDs for different economic indicators
Some metros use S&P Case-Shiller Home Price Index (monthly, ends in 'XRSA' or 'XRNSA')
Some metros use FHFA Home Price Index (quarterly, starts with 'ATNHPIUS' and ends in 'Q')
MSA Population and Civilian Population are set manually and not pulled from APIs
Census Code is used for reference and is set manually
